                     <interp inst="t18430508-1452-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18430508-cd-50" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18430508-1452-offence-1 t18430508-cd-50"></join>28th of April</rs>, at <placeName id="t18430508-geo-14">
